{
  "$id": "phase-gate",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "schema",
    "gate",
    "verdict",
    "criteria"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "schema": {
      "const": "phase-gate"
    },
    "gate": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "verdict": {
      "enum": [
        "PASS",
        "FAIL"
      ]
    },
    "criteria": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "pass": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "evidence": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "risks": {
      "type": "array"
    },
    "carry_over": {
      "type": "array"
    }
  },
  "_note": "文档形态;运行时校验为 src-tauri/src/services/nexus_verdict.rs 的必填字段轻量校验,两者须同步维护。qa-verdict 组合 id 在校验层按 schema 字段分派到 qa-pass/qa-fail。"
}